            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 4625,
            "text": "{\"id\":\"msg_01ATqYtERukPqvagPt9cn3wZ\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"model\":\"claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01AvS6jqQzu769hHJjUQTthT\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"code\":\"import { Card } from \\\"@/components/ui/card\\\"\\nimport { Tooltip, TooltipContent, TooltipProvider, TooltipTrigger } from \\\"@/components/ui/tooltip\\\"\\n\\nexport function SocialProof() {\\n  return (\\n    <section id=\\\"SocialProof\\\" className=\\\"w-full py-16 bg-accent\\\">\\n      <div className=\\\"container mx-auto px-4\\\">\\n        {/* Header */}\\n        <div className=\\\"text-center mb-12\\\">\\n          <h2 className=\\\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-accent-foreground\\\">\\n            Partners in Excellence\\n          </h2>\\n          <p className=\\\"text-accent-foreground-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto\\\">\\n            Our groundbreaking space exploration initiatives are powered by collaborations with the world's most innovative space organizations.\\n          </p>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        {/* Stats */}\\n        <div className=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto\\\">\\n          <Card className=\\\"p-6 text-center bg-accent/10 border-accent-foreground/20\\\">\\n            <p className=\\\"text-3xl font-bold text-accent-foreground\\\">3+</p>\\n            <p className=\\\"text-accent-foreground-muted\\\">Major Space Research Partnerships</p>\\n          </Card>\\n          <Card className=\\\"p-6 text-center bg-accent/10 border-accent-foreground/20\\\">\\n            <p className=\\\"text-3xl font-bold text-accent-foreground\\\">Global</p>\\n            <p className=\\\"text-accent-foreground-muted\\\">Collaborative Network</p>\\n          </Card>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        {/* Partner Logos */}\\n        <div className=\\\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\\\">\\n          <TooltipProvider>\\n            {/* NASA Space Apps Challenge */}\\n            <Tooltip>\\n              <TooltipTrigger asChild>\\n                <Card className=\\\"p-8 flex items-center justify-center bg-accent/10 border-accent-foreground/20 hover:bg-accent/20 transition-colors cursor-pointer\\\">\\n                  <p className=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-accent-foreground text-center\\\">\\n                    NASA Space Apps Challenge\\n                  </p>\\n                </Card>\\n              </TooltipTrigger>\\n              <TooltipContent>\\n                <p className=\\\"text-sm\\\">Official participant in NASA's global innovation program</p>\\n              </TooltipContent>\\n            </Tooltip>\\n\\n            {/* European Space Agency */}\\n            <Tooltip>\\n              <TooltipTrigger asChild>\\n                <Card className=\\\"p-8 flex items-center justify-center bg-accent/10 border-accent-foreground/20 hover:bg-accent/20 transition-colors cursor-pointer\\\">\\n                  <p className=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-accent-foreground text-center\\\">\\n                    European Space Agency\\n                  </p>\\n                </Card>\\n              </TooltipTrigger>\\n              <TooltipContent>\\n                <p className=\\\"text-sm\\\">Research collaboration partner with ESA</p>\\n              </TooltipContent>\\n            </Tooltip>\\n\\n            {/* SpaceX */}\\n            <Tooltip>\\n              <TooltipTrigger asChild>\\n                <Card className=\\\"p-8 flex items-center justify-center bg-accent/10 border-accent-foreground/20 hover:bg-accent/20 transition-colors cursor-pointer\\\">\\n                  <p className=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-accent-foreground text-center\\\">\\n                    SpaceX Collaborative Research Initiative\\n                  </p>\\n                </Card>\\n              </TooltipTrigger>\\n              <TooltipContent>\\n                <p className=\\\"text-sm\\\">Active research partnership with SpaceX</p>\\n              </TooltipContent>\\n            </Tooltip>\\n          </TooltipProvider>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n  )\\n}\",\"summary\":\"Created a SocialProof section component that showcases partnerships with major space organizations. The component features a clean, modern design using the accent color scheme with proper semantic color utilities. It includes partner logos displayed as interactive cards with tooltips, and key statistics presented in a grid layout. The design is fully responsive and uses ShadcnUI components as suggested.\",\"dependencies\":[]}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":4932,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":1140,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
